definitions.definition: ( archaic or historical ) A person who writes for a gazette or newspaper ; a journalist ; ( specifically ) a journalist engaged by a government .
( by extension , obsolete ) A gazette, a newspaper.

main_definition: ( archaic or historical ) A person who writes for a gazette or newspaper ; a journalist ; ( specifically ) a journalist engaged by a government .
secondary_definitions: ( by extension , obsolete ) A gazette, a newspaper.

definitions.definition: A dictionary or index of geographical locations .
A similar descriptive list (often alphabetical ) of information on other subjects .
